name: Dulwich Delivers
description: With over 100 listings, Dulwich Delivers helps connect those at home with local businesses in South East London, whether in Dulwich, Brockley, Brixton, or beyond. As well as bread, milk, coffee, and veg boxes, you can now order East Dulwich kimchi, sourdough starter, Peckham-made hand sanitiser, or cans of mead. You can find someone to pick up and drop off prescriptions, get compost for your garden, or have a bespoke desk designed and delivered, all contact-free. You can get pictures framed and jewellery repaired, and you can rent toys and gym equipment by the week from businesses who are doing their utmost to enable you to stay safe at home and save lives.
